{"tid":1394922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【重要討論】點樣先可以maximize公務員罷工嘅impact？","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T07:04:05.000Z","uid":266060,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4b52b32459ef982301f07a418d414bb8d699ed97","tid":1394922,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"政府今日鬧公務員罷工，反映咗公務員集體造反，可以有效地打擊政府嘅管治認受性。<br />\n<br />\n問題係，星期一公務員罷工之後，點樣quantify同maximize個impact？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/about/govdirectory/govchart/images/chart.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout%2Fgovdirectory%2Fgovchart%2Fimages%2Fchart.gif&h=3101bd49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/about/govdirectory/govchart/index.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout%2Fgovdirectory%2Fgovchart%2Findex.htm&d=BmTzKXBjX6ru83xd6aIIEfkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=cd4dca7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/about/govdirectory/govchart/index.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇可能用3司13局67個部門做單位<br />\n只要有人參加罷工（即使一個都得），就等如嗰個部門有人罷工<br />\n8月5當日用google form之類即時收集，以職員證為憑證<br />\n當中盡快（如中午）公布「3司1X局5X個部門都有人響應了罷工」之類？"},{"pid":"fe45a53aa963fa9d373e362e9dcf8a662293eb6b","tid":1394922,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2cdce589f4acc155a7bfc1b3f41171a5b6f00f","tid":1394922,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2456dcd297d7af838c1ba82f487bd7fc3cb23c8","tid":1394922,"uid":266060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:47:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce374c47d9517a2c9a9001ae8be7b4b8ab062ba","tid":1394922,"u